        <p> In the last weeks / months of my trip I will start to search for new jobs in Europe more intensively. When I got back to Sydney, I want to sell the camper van and slowly prepare for my return trip. So make Australian tax returns, unsubscribe an account if no longer needs and what else is part of it. If nothing shifts in time, the plan is to fly towards Hamburg again at the end of April 2013. </p>
